  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Beauty & Wellness</li><li>Position Title: <strong>TCM Practitioner</strong></li><li>Working Location: Orchard Road</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days, 10am – 8pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $4000 (Basic) + Commission + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver customized advice on sub-health management and physical wellness utilizing Traditional Chinese Medicine (TCM) principles tailored to individual customer needs.</li><li>Administer facial acupuncture treatments targeting anti-aging, skin brightening, acne management, facial contouring, and other cosmetic enhancements.</li><li>Conduct independent TCM consultations and execute appropriate treatments.</li><li>Work collaboratively with beauticians and other team members, adhering to company's standardized procedures and customer service guidelines.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>A recognised Degree or Postgraduate qualification in Traditional Chinese Medicine</li><li>Registration with the Traditional Chinese Medicine Practitioners Board of Singapore (TCMPB).</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77338 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
